		<title>06SPORTS DAY, ETTRICK VALLEY.</title>
		<content> The first Saturday in August attracts 
 many locals, visitors and exiles to   
 the annual sports day.It is held in a 
 field beside the school and the Boston
 Hall and is open to all comers.       
 Events for adults and children are    
 viewed from rows of straw bales, and  
 are accompanied by competitions.      
 The highlight of the afternoon is a   
 lavish picnic tea provided by the     
 sports committee.                     
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
